text: Taihe () is a town under the administration of Nanfeng County, Jiangxi, China. , it has one residential community and 10 villages under its administration. == Administrative divisions == Taihe administers the following villages and communities: Communities: * Taihe Community Villages: * Taihe Village * Dianqian * Xiayang * Danyang * Kangdu * Weifang * Xiatong * Siqian * Hangshan * Qianfang == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Jiangxi Category:Nanfeng County
